{{italic title}}
'''''POL Oxygen''''' was an international design, art and architecture quarterly magazine. The magazine existed between 2001 and 2008.<ref>{{cite web|title=POL Oxygen magazine|url=http://www.theloop.com.au/one8one7/portfolio/pol-oxygen-magazine/6102|publisher=The Loop|accessdate=10 November 2015}}</ref> It contained extended profiles that look at the lives, ideas and work of people working internationally. It was edited in [[Sydney]], art directed in [[London]], printed in [[Hong Kong]] and distributed worldwide. 

